snippet.title: CAR DETAILING SIMULATOR - OFFICIAL RELEASE DATE | Steam
snippet.description:
Car Detailing Simulator will be released on APRIL 13, 2022!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1433570/Car_Detailing_Simulator/

YES! It's coming next month! 🥳 Together with the release of the full version of the game, you will be able to purchase the AMMO NYC DLC by Larry Kosilly!
